Shanda Aims to Achieve 20% Revenue from Overseas in 3 Years

-- B y   H u i w e n   Y a n g
-- 
2011-06-01T04:30:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-01/shanda-aims-to-achieve-20-revenue-from-overseas-in-3-years.html
Shanda Games Ltd. (GAME) ,  China ’s
third-biggest provider of online games, targets overseas
business to make up 20 percent of total revenue in three
years, Chief Executive Officer Alan Tan said in an
interview in  Shanghai  today.  He expects mobile games to account for 10 percent of
overall revenue in about three years and sees the company’s
growth outpacing overall growth of the gaming market in
China, Tan said. 